35
00:06:42,126 --> 00:06:43,676
Take off the headphone.

36
00:06:47,131 --> 00:06:48,691
Spit the gum.

37
00:06:50,735 --> 00:06:51,895
Get out.

38
00:06:57,441 --> 00:06:59,911
We're Wonder Boys!

39
00:07:07,284 --> 00:07:08,444
Where's Mr. Children?

40
00:07:09,987 --> 00:07:12,147
I came to see them.

41
00:07:13,591 --> 00:07:14,561
Sign this.

42
00:07:14,792 --> 00:07:17,852
You'll be a director
and a shareholder.

43
00:07:18,195 --> 00:07:22,355
We can't sell Mr. Children.
They're out of date.

44
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:28,570
Well, I totally understand.
You've been alienated for long.

45
00:07:28,706 --> 00:07:31,766
It's gonna be much easier than
Mr. Children.

46
00:07:32,410 --> 00:07:37,470
Just try half as hard.
Then I'll do the rest.

47
00:07:39,216 --> 00:07:43,676
You mean Mr. Children
doesn't get second chance?

48
00:07:43,821 --> 00:07:49,381
