bust-up fees.

53
00:08:04,975 --> 00:08:07,735
Send me a document
proving the breach of contract.

54
00:08:07,845 --> 00:08:11,105
From now on,
I'll work with Mr. Children.

55
00:08:11,649 --> 00:08:16,279
It's losing game.
You're gonna be tapped out.

56
00:08:18,389 --> 00:08:24,259
- Do as I say, it's better...
- No thanks.

57
00:08:25,296 --> 00:08:27,156
I'll work on my own.

58
00:08:27,398 --> 00:08:28,958
Are you throwing
down the gauntlet?

59
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:33,470
You didn't know?
I've already started the game.

60
00:08:38,209 --> 00:08:39,769
Are you leaving for real?

61
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:41,780
Do you have a plan?

62
00:08:43,214 --> 00:08:46,274
Find the members
and set an office.

63
00:08:46,717 --> 00:08:50,377
Think again.
You could lose big.

64
00:08:50,621 --> 00:08:51,781
Listen!

65
00:08:52,323 --> 00:08:56,493
