- Hello.

137
00:16:28,812 --> 00:16:36,582
If you have some memory
of that time, please tell us.

138
00:16:38,622 --> 00:16:43,182
I remember a lamppost
in an alley.

139
00:16:44,728 --> 00:16:47,088
I was three years old.

140
00:16:48,031 --> 00:16:53,401
