142
00:16:57,841 --> 00:16:59,501
Ms. O?

143
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:16,160
I miss the time.
If you ever feel sad...

144
00:17:18,895 --> 00:17:24,655
You want me to dance?
I can't even lift a baby for long.

145
00:17:25,502 --> 00:17:28,162
Hyun, clean room no. 5!

146
00:17:28,405 --> 00:17:31,855
What are you doing?
You lazy ass!

147
00:17:35,112 --> 00:17:36,982
I want to dance again.

148
00:17:56,233 --> 00:17:57,893
Stop it!

149
00:17:58,635 --> 00:18:00,095
I'm sick of you.

150
00:18:06,276 --> 00:18:07,736
It's over.

151
00:18:11,882 --> 00:18:13,652
Jio.

152
00:18:21,191 --> 00:18:23,561
Oh, you all came!

153
00:18:31,001 --> 00:18:32,261
What's this place?

154
00:18:33,603 --> 00:18:34,663
Do you do boxing?

155
00:18:35,739 --> 00:18:41,009
No, it's for you.
It'll be a good dancing floor.

156
00:18:41,311 --> 00:18:43,871
Do we have a lead singer?

157
00:18:45,015 --> 00:18:47,775
A singer who will
dump us again?

158
00:18:50,020 --> 00:18:52,080
Jio, don't say...

159
00:18:54,124 --> 00:18:57,294
Anyway, I'm happy to
see you guys together.

160
00:18:57,828 --> 00:19:03,318
Remember HWANG?
You'll perform in his show.

161
00:19:04,768 --> 00:19:05,828
Have you talked to him?

162
00:19:06,470 --> 00:19:10,460
No, you make an arrangement.
President PARK.

163
00:19:11,374 --> 00:19:15,444
President PARK?
Who, me?

164
00:19:15,679 --> 00:19:17,649
I handed in your resignation.

165
00:19:17,781 --> 00:19:19,651
Letter of Resignation
O Gu-ju and PARK Sang-sik

166
00:19:19,783 --> 00:19:22,053
You little...

167
00:19:23,787 --> 00:19:25,477
President PARK?

168
00:19:26,690 --> 00:19:28,350
A Cottage on a Grassland

169
00:19:29,292 --> 00:19:35,662
I wish my words

170
00:19:35,899 --> 00:19:48,279
stay in your heart
like an old picture.

171
00:19:48,512 --> 00:19:50,172
Knock it out.

172
00:19:51,815 --> 00:19:54,275
I'm having a conversation here.

173
00:19:56,520 --> 00:19:59,180
We're going on an audition
this Saturday.

174
00:19:59,623 --> 00:20:01,593
I feel good about it.

175
00:20:03,426 --> 00:20:07,186
I bought your outfits.
Look, they're expensive!

176
00:20:07,430 --> 00:20:09,990
So don't expect your back pay.

177
00:20:11,735 --> 00:20:13,995
- No way!
- Hey, guys.

178
00:20:14,137 --> 00:20:16,797
If you do well in audition
and become a star...

179
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,710
I'm giving you loads of
money.

180
00:20:18,842 --> 00:20:22,402
Believe me boys.
You all wear size 100.

181
00:20:22,646 --> 00:20:25,506
I mean, even your sizes
prove you're a team!

182
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:29,910
- You don't feel it?
- I don't feel it.

183
00:20:41,164 --> 00:20:45,034
I'm a Ioner.
I'm a Ioner.

184
00:20:45,168 --> 00:20:47,398
Don't you love me?

185
00:20:47,404 --> 00:20:49,134
What I can do?

186
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:05,290
We're looking for boys.

187
00:21:05,722 --> 00:21:07,092
Ok, but we'll just do it.

188
00:21:12,629 --> 00:21:16,219
Mimicking

189
00:21:16,399 --> 00:21:20,099
Will you marry me?

190
00:21:24,841 --> 00:21:26,601
Where are all the good ones?

191
00:21:27,043 --> 00:21:32,003
Mr. SA has set his audition
on the same time as ours.

192
00:21:32,849 --> 00:21:38,519
I will not say
that I am sorry.

193
00:21:38,655 --> 00:21:39,815
Next!

194
00:21:48,365 --> 00:21:49,725
Are you the member?

195
00:21:49,866 --> 00:21:51,416
I'm the manager.

196
00:22:11,721 --> 00:22:13,991
What are you doing here?

197
00:22:14,624 --> 00:22:15,784
Are you a team?

198
00:22:16,226 --> 00:22:20,816
- We're the underground band.
- "Rebel Without a Cause."

199
00:22:21,531 --> 00:22:22,501
Start.

200
00:22:41,051 --> 00:22:47,011
I wish my words

201
00:22:48,258 --> 00:23:00,428
sink into you
and touch your heart.

202
00:23:02,706 --> 00:23:03,866
Stop!

203
00:23:23,927 --> 00:23:25,287
You want stronger beat?

204
00:23:26,029 --> 00:23:26,999
Faster?

205
00:23:27,831 --> 00:23:29,091
Solo.

206
00:23:32,736 --> 00:23:34,286
We're okay.

207
00:23:40,243 --> 00:23:44,613
The sound of a warm breeze.

208
00:23:45,148 --> 00:23:51,108
Comes to me and comforts me.

209
00:23:52,155 --> 00:23:55,315
I feel sweet.

210
00:23:55,558 --> 00:23:59,318
Happy as in a dream.

211
00:23:59,863 --> 00:24:05,063
I can smile because of you.

212
00:24:07,203 --> 00:24:08,863
Summer dream.

213
00:24:09,105 --> 00:24:14,165
The sweet melody.

214
00:24:14,411 --> 00:24:16,071
Feel your dream.

215
00:24:16,212 --> 00:24:21,482
We will stay together.

216
00:24:22,318 --> 00:24:24,578
It may break your heart.

217
00:24:24,721 --> 00:24:28,181
It may bring you down.

218
00:24:28,324 --> 00:24:31,384
But you have me.

219
00:24:31,628 --> 00:24:38,588
We'll dream forever.

220
00:24:39,135 --> 00:24:40,495
He's out of breath.

221
00:24:45,642 --> 00:24:47,802
What a mantrap.

222
00:24:48,344 --> 00:24:49,714
You suck.

223
00:24:50,246 --> 00:24:52,906
Poor, rough and dull.

224
00:24:53,049 --> 00:24:58,319
You're self-indulgent.
There's just your voice.

225
00:25:00,557 --> 00:25:02,247
But I can hear it.

226
00:25:02,992 --> 00:25:06,452
You can't be a star
unless you work with me.

227
00:25:09,299 --> 00:25:12,669
Only me?
Isn't it a band audition?

228
00:25:13,503 --> 00:25:15,273
Why do you say like that?

229
00:25:15,405 --> 00:25:16,765
We need a lead singer.

230
00:25:19,409 --> 00:25:22,969
We need a singer
for a idol pop group.

231
00:25:23,112 --> 00:25:24,582
I won't do it.

232
00:25:24,814 --> 00:25:28,984
As you can see,
we are a band.

233
00:25:29,719 --> 00:25:31,379
Hope you find the right one.

234
00:25:38,928 --> 00:25:44,088
I'm going to take a train
and go to the countryside.

235
00:25:45,134 --> 00:25:47,604
You know, I always
wanted to be a farmer.

236
00:25:47,737 --> 00:25:49,707
Band without a bassist?

237
00:25:51,741 --> 00:25:53,501
Are you leaving too?

238
00:25:53,643 --> 00:25:56,613
I had a job interview,
yesterday.

239
00:25:57,747 --> 00:26:02,337
My girlfriend wants me
to work at some company.

240
00:26:03,786 --> 00:26:05,846
Her father runs it.

241
00:26:06,089 --> 00:26:07,149
Come on!!

242
00:26:08,291 --> 00:26:14,161
We rebel without a cause,
not betray without a cause!

243
00:26:28,912 --> 00:26:30,472
Eat when it's hot.

244
00:26:34,350 --> 00:26:36,010
Excuse me.

245
00:26:38,321 --> 00:26:41,381
I don't understand.

246
00:26:41,524 --> 00:26:46,294
Why is hers and mine
so different in quantity?

247
00:26:46,529 --> 00:26:48,389
She's a regular.

248
00:26:50,133 --> 00:26:52,003
I see.

249
00:27:02,378 --> 00:27:10,648
Run as fast as you can,
little boy.

250
00:27:10,787 --> 00:27:15,877
If you look back now,
you will give up...

251
00:27:25,802 --> 00:27:30,572
He is a freelance worker
doing several jobs.

252
00:27:31,007 --> 00:27:34,877
A coffee shop part-timer,
a chauffeur and a performer.

253
00:27:35,011 --> 00:27:38,281
You know, he was
a trainee in Star Music.

254
00:27:38,414 --> 00:27:43,784
SA wanted to make a band
few years ago, remember?

255
00:27:44,220 --> 00:27:46,690
He was kicked out
for his bad attitude.

256
00:28:06,876 --> 00:28:08,336
Caramel Macchiato.

257
00:28:14,083 --> 00:28:15,743
Work with me.

258
00:28:23,593 --> 00:28:24,653
Here.

259
00:28:30,299 --> 00:28:31,269
You're born to be a singer.

260
00:28:31,401 --> 00:28:32,371
How much?

261
00:28:32,502 --> 00:28:33,562
Work with me!

262
00:28:36,406 --> 00:28:39,266
Hello, where should I go?

263
00:28:43,613 --> 00:28:44,983
Miss...

264
00:28:45,515 --> 00:28:46,975
Tunnel No.1.

265
00:28:48,017 --> 00:28:49,277
Are you stalking me?

266
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:52,590
