536
00:55:24,412 --> 00:55:30,782
Comes to me and comforts me.

537
00:55:31,319 --> 00:55:34,579
I feel sweet.

538
00:55:35,123 --> 00:55:37,093
Happy as in a dream.

539
00:55:44,932 --> 00:55:48,892
- Calm down, please.
- Stay away.

540
00:55:55,943 --> 00:55:57,413
Dad!

541
00:55:57,545 --> 00:56:00,705
You say you're a dancer?
You can't even dodge.

542
00:56:01,282 --> 00:56:04,552
