- You're lying.

553
00:57:26,100 --> 00:57:28,860
People say...

554
00:57:30,004 --> 00:57:33,064
you hear a chime bell
when you kiss someone?

555
00:57:35,510 --> 00:57:37,880
That could be
the death knell.

556
00:57:44,218 --> 00:57:45,978
Are you crazy?

557
00:57:49,824 --> 00:57:51,384
I can't feel anything.

558
00:58:25,393 --> 00:58:28,163
I really want Mr. Children
to come to my school!

559
00:58:39,407 --> 00:58:41,667
Horse Chestnut Park

560
00:58:41,809 --> 00:58:43,469
The most expected
boy group of the year!

561
00:58:43,611 --> 00:58:45,981
Mr. Children!
Summer Dream.

